      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·014.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泉水.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>毖彼泉水，亦流于淇，有懷于衞，靡日不思，孌彼諸姬，聊與之謀。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How the water bubbles up from that spring,
And flows away to the K'e!
My heart is in Wei;
There is not a day I do not think of it.
Admirable are those, my cousins;
I will take counsel with them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-014__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">guofeng-beifeng-014</prop>
