      <prop type="x-segment-type">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·014.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泉水.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>出宿于泲，飲餞于禰，女子有行，遠父母兄弟，問我諸姑，遂及伯姊。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When I came forth, I lodged in Tse,
And we drank the cup of convoy at Ne.
When a young lady goes to be married,
She leaves her parents and brothers;
[But] I would ask for my aunts,
And then for my elder sister.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-014__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
