      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·014.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泉水.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>出宿于干，飲餞于言，載脂載舝，還車言邁，遄臻于衞，不瑕有害。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I will go forth and lodge in Kan,
And we will drink the cup of convoy at Yen.
I will grease the axle and fix the pin,
And the returning chariot will proceed.
Quickly shall we arrive in Wei; —
But would not this be wrong?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-014__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
