      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·014.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泉水.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我思肥泉，茲之永歎，思須與漕，我心悠悠，駕言出遊，以寫我憂。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I think of the Fei-ts'euen,
I am ever sighing about it.
I think of Seu and Ts'aou,
Long, long, my heart dwells with them.
Let me drive forth and travel there,
To dissipate my sorrow.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
